{
  "texts": [
    "As shown in Table 3, EDSR and RRDB models are trained exclusively using reconstruction losses, which results in subpar performance when evaluated based on the perceptual LPIPS metric.",
    "In contrast, our SRDDGAN model outperforms ESRGAN, which utilizes GANs in terms of PSNR, LPIPS, and LR-PSNR.",
    "Notably, SRDDGAN achieves the highest score in LR-PSNR among all other models; 2.",
    "In Fig. 7, it was noted that EDSR and RRDB produced unsatisfactory visualizations due to their inadequate generation of high-frequency details.",
    "Conversely, SRDDGAN surpassed SRDiff in perceptual quality by generating rich and detailed visualizations."
  ]
}